    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-08-17T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-08-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="277"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d277">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Eustis</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-08-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 17, 1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>What action on urgent demands in Waller case telegraphed July 31? If evidence
                    still withheld or access to the prisoner denied, it is due to this Government
                    that the reasons be plainly stated.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Adee</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Acting Secretary</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
